 |  publisher = [[Interscope Records]]
 |       date = 
 |        url = 
 |     format = 
 |         id = 
 | accessdate = 2008-02-24
 |      quote = 
 }}</ref> The following day, due to the [[9/11]] [[terrorist attacks]] in [[New York City]] and [[Washington D.C.]], the promotional schedule for the album was put on hold.<ref>{{cite journal
 | quotes = 
 | last = 
 | first = 
 | authorlink = 
 | coauthors = 
