In October, ''Beautiful Garbage'' achieved a #13 debut on the Billboard 200,<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.allbusiness.com/retail-trade/miscellaneous-retail-retail-stores-not/4394299-1.html | title=Ja Rule Feeling No 'Pain' With No. 1 Bow | publisher=AllBusiness.com (originally published by Billboard) | accessdate=2007-12-14}}</ref> as well as reaching #6 on the [[Top Internet Albums]] chart and topping the Electronic Albums chart for seven weeks. In its first three months on sale, ''Beautiful Garbage'' sold 1.2 million copies.<ref>{{cite video
